These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, july, may
There 4 different types of food: potato, pineapple, cherry, pepper
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, rock-climbing, video-games, reading
City: miami, boston, london, colone
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person eating pepper##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in may##2
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person traveling to london is the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Birthday   | november | may   | december  | july  |
| Food   | pineapple    | pepper    | potato      | cherry    |
| Hobby   | reading | rock-climbing | video-games | singing |
| City     | colone  | miami       | boston    | london     |

