.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
City: marseilles, hannover, boston, berlin
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, prince, baccarat, cain
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, fanta, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, dressmaker, librarian, manager
1. the manager is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is the dressmaker##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the cain-smoker is between the person drinking fanta and the fisherman##2
6. the manager is between the cain-smoker and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
8. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
9. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| City         | berlin | hannover    | boston  | marseilles    |
| Cigar   | bolivar      | prince  | cain  | baccarat |
| Beverage           | mirinda      | fanta       | iced-tea      | lemonade       |
| Job         | dressmaker    | manager | librarian | fisherman |

