.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, sprite, mirinda
4 different games are played: go, canasta, billiard, snooker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, zinnia, balloon-flower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, thriller, mystery, documentary
1. the person who growszinnia is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person who growssunflower is the person playing snooker##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person playing go and the person playing snooker##2
9. the person playing billiard is between the person drinking sprite and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage        | water | sprite     | almond-milk   | mirinda     |
| Game       | canasta   | go   | billiard | snooker |
| Flower         | rose   | zinnia | balloon-flower       | sunflower    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | thriller | fantasy  | documentary    |

