The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, electronic, soul, r&b
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, tulip, begonia
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, argentine, canadian, malaysian
 1. the fan electronic is on the far right##1
 2. the fan r&b is the person eating cauliflower##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the malaysian##1
 4. the spanish is on the far left##1
 5. the fan r&b is the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the spanish##1
 7. the fan electronic is the person eating artichoke##1
 8. the fan trance is on the right of the fan r&b##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the argentine##1
10. the person eating raspberry is between the person who growsiris and the person eating garlic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Food           | cauliflower  | garlic | raspberry     | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | trance  | soul | electronic       |
| Flower           | rose       | begonia    | tulip      | iris           |
| Nationality         | spanish | argentine   | malaysian   | canadian         |

