.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, may, february
City: colone, rome, miami, hamburg
House: wooden, craftsman, futuristic, farmhouse
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, ebony, lilac, apricot
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is the craftsman house##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who likes apricot and the wooden house##2
10. the futuristic house is the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday          | april         | may         | november     | february      |
| City           | miami | hamburg | colone    | rome     |
| House   | wooden      | futuristic       | farmhouse    | craftsman       |
| Color         | white     | lilac       | apricot | ebony |

