5. the person driving the tram is the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday           | september | november | april  | december |
