House: cottage, tower, ranch-style, modern
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, aquamarine, coral, blue
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the frog##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes coral##1
 3. the owner of the frog is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the modern house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the tower house is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the rat and the person who likes brown##2
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | may        | april    | february | june   |
| Pet           | rat | fish | lizard   | frog |
| House   | ranch-style         | cottage       | modern      | tower     |
| Color         | coral       | blue | brown    | aquamarine  |

