 1. the dannemann-smoker is between the person driving the car and the old-henry-smoker##2
 2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the chef##1
 3. the person driving the ship is between the person playing chess and the person playing backgammon##2
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the social-worker##1
